# AI & Project Management Conference 2026

## Overview

The **AI & Project Management Conference 2026** brings together project managers, technology leaders, AI practitioners, and business professionals to explore how artificial intelligence is transforming project delivery, governance, and decision-making.

Attendees will gain practical insights through keynote presentations, expert-led workshops, panel discussions, and real-world case studies covering the latest trends in AI-powered project management.

## Event Details

* **Date:** September 15–16, 2026
* **Time:** 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM
* **Location:** Bengaluru, India
* **Format:** In-person with live online streaming

## Key Topics

* AI in Project Planning and Scheduling
* Risk Management with AI
* Predictive Analytics for Project Success
* Agile and AI Integration
* Generative AI for Documentation
* Automation with AI Agents
* Project Portfolio Management
* AI Governance and Ethics

